IELTS Exam Preparation

Ace your IELTS Academic or General Training exam

Comprehensive IELTS preparation for both Academic and General Training modules.

IELTS Modules We Cover

IELTS Academic

Designed for students applying to universities or professional registration. We cover academic reading, writing, listening, and speaking.

Perfect for:

  • • University applications
  • • Professional registration
  • • Academic study abroad
  • • Higher education programs

IELTS General Training

Focused on migration, work, or training programs. Lessons include everyday communication tasks and real-life scenarios.

Perfect for:

  • • Work visas
  • • Immigration applications
  • • Training programs
  • • Secondary education

Band Scores & Success

Band 6.0

Competent user with good control of familiar topics.

Band 6.5

Good user with minor inaccuracies but effective communication.

Band 7.0

Good user using complex language with flexibility.

Band 7.5+

Very good user expressing precise meaning with few errors.

What You'll Learn in IELTS Lessons

Reading & Listening

  • • Time management strategies for each section
  • • Understanding question types and techniques
  • • Building academic vocabulary
  • • Note-taking and skimming skills
  • • Practice with official IELTS materials

Writing & Speaking

  • • Task 1 and Task 2 writing strategies
  • • Speaking test format and preparation
  • • Pronunciation and fluency improvement
  • • Grammar for academic writing
  • • Mock tests with detailed feedback
